93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:02): the best way to approach women is to be bold really
93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:03): talk to them, find out what they like and don't like, try to be more than just a friend
93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:04): whether you're looking for a girlfriend or just sex, you have to take a chance and say something

93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:05): a thousand mile journey starts with the first step
93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:05): worry about just starting a conversation with them first thing
93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:05): from there, just try to keep it flowing
93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:06): another important thing is to get close

93d7fda6184bbbd3b5d735fba06dc34e (16:07): your supervisors at work and your teachers also maintain a much bigger distance
